What exactly do you expect to find on that thing?

It's a friggin' shuttle. No doomsday devices or death
rays or cloaking devices or ANY SPECIAL GIZMOS worth
taking. It will in no way turn the tide of your little
war here. It's a standard ordinary Decepticon shuttle
armed with plain, standard issue blasters. The
shuttles themselves were indended as a plot device, a
prop, nothing more.
